Package: artimagen
Title: AI Image Generation and Editing Toolkit
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R:
    person("Bobby", "Fatemi", , "bobby@artalytics.app", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for AI-assisted image generation and editing for digital
    artists, including region-aware editing and tiled super-resolution. Built
    to sit on top of the Artalytics Gemini client (artgemini). Functions are
    introduced under an experimental lifecycle and graduate to stable as they
    settle.
